e news broke, the U.S. Navy&rsquo;s doomsday planes launched on both American coasts.<br />\n<br />\n<ins>The E-6B Mercury is one of the Pentagon&rsquo;s airborne nuclear command posts. The four-engine planes&mdash;derivatives of the Boeing 707 airliner&mdash;carry special communication systems and crews for commanding the Navy&rsquo;s Ohio-class nuclear ballistic-missile submarines.</ins><br />\n帶住通信系統 指揮 俄亥級核子彈道潛艦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI<ins><span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">n an atomic war, the E-6s would relay directions to the Ohio boomers, helping the boats&rsquo; crews to target enemy cities and military bases with nuclear-tipped Trident submarine-launched ballistic missiles, or SLBMs.</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHogan tracked the E-6s on public software that registers airplanes&rsquo; radio transponders.<ins> Military planes often switch off their transponders in order to avoid being tracked. If a military jet&rsquo;s transponders are on, it&rsquo;s because their crews want to be seen.</ins><br />\n<br />\nIn the case of the E-6s, &ldquo;it's a message to the small group of adversaries with SLBMs and ICBMs,&rdquo; Hogan noted. The Pentagon apparently wants atomic-armed rivals of the United States&mdash;Russia, China and North Korea&mdash;<ins>to know that America&rsquo;s nuclear command system is intact, even if the commander-in-chief might be sick.</ins>"},{"pid":"591d2a9bdd4dd95b779befce4314e0f42a6bb45c","tid":2226643,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8ad8f7abd5723186404a3d7a1f559ba5485f1d3","tid":2226643,"uid":4783,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"faf2843fe170de7f0879f0b5e4fcb8f34c9b4f9b","tid":2226643,"uid":39365,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"因為總統中左武肺所以戰略核武要升空預備？純吹水，唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T08:43:28.000Z","msg":"警告黎<br />\n警告所有同美國敵對既人／組織<br />\n美國仍然保有mad能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntrump病左，都可以射核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}